    "v4 task model: test_objects declare mandatory test_types and transport_options.",
    "FPP per-die: die0, die2, die4 have FPP; die1, die3, die5 use serial TAP only. Odd-layer dies lack FPP hardware.",
    "Per-die BIST engines: 4 out of 6 dies have BIST-capable targets, each with its own engine.",
    "Deeper stack creates more STAP bypass overhead for far-end dies.",
    "6-die stack with longer serial chain makes TAP bottleneck more pronounced, giving BIST interleaving more room for gain.",
    "Thermal RC parameters escalate with stack depth."
